{"id":651742,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/08/【立此存照】朋友圈确实容易给人一种偏激印象/","date":"2020-08-05T10:17:06Z","modified":"2020-08-06T01:55:39Z","title":"【立此存照】朋友圈确实给人一种“偏激印象”","content":"<p>8月5日，封面新闻报道了“南京女生月月被杀案”事件进展，警方认定其男友洪某及两名同伙有着作案嫌疑。据悉，洪某曾“自称是官二代，在保密公司工作”，还给“月月的亲属谢琳”留下了一种“偏激”印象。封面新闻在报道的新闻视频中截取了洪某的多条微信朋友圈，有网友发现在月月失踪（7月9日遇害）之后洪某朋友圈仍转发了大量“战狼新闻”，重点关注反美议题。在月月“失踪”后，男友洪某还与月月父亲一同去警局报案。</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_651745\" style=\"width: 510px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-651745\" class=\"wp-image-651745 size-full\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/月月.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"273\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/月月.jpg 500w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/月月-300x164.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-651745\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">被害女生月月</p></div>\n<p>@封面新闻：【#南京女生被杀案嫌犯身份#：自称官二代、保密部门上班，不让女友发朋友圈】8月4日晚，西双版纳州勐海县公安局发布通报，经调查寻找，失联25天的南京女大学生月月，已于7月9日晚，被其男友洪某伙同张某光、曹某青，诱骗至勐海县城郊山林杀害并埋尸。<strong>事发后，还曾和月月父亲一起找人。</strong>月月的亲属谢琳曾见过洪某，在她和月月面前<strong>，“洪某自称是官二代，在保密公司工作”</strong>，谢琳说，洪某给自己的印象，很偏激，让人害怕。洪某不允许月月在朋友暴露自己的身份。一份疑似洪某朋友圈截图显示，洪某的朋友圈几乎每天都在更新，除了月月遇害当天。 封面新闻<a href=\"https://weibo.com/tv/show/1034:4534590832836615\">微博视频</a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-651746\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/封面新闻1.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"725\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/封面新闻1.png 1166w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/封面新闻1-207x300.png 207w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/封面新闻1-706x1024.png 706w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/封面新闻1-768x1113.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/封面新闻1-1060x1536.png 1060w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/封面新闻1-1080x1565.png 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /> <img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-651747\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/封面新闻2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"668\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/封面新闻2.png 1152w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/封面新闻2-224x300.png 224w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/封面新闻2-766x1024.png 766w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/封面新闻2-768x1027.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/封面新闻2-1149x1536.png 1149w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/封面新闻2-1080x1444.png 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-651744\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/朋友圈2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"625\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/朋友圈2.png 1242w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/朋友圈2-240x300.png 240w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/朋友圈2-819x1024.png 819w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/朋友圈2-768x960.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/朋友圈2-1229x1536.png 1229w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/朋友圈2-1080x1350.png 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-651743\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/朋友圈1.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"611\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/朋友圈1.png 1258w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/朋友圈1-245x300.png 245w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/朋友圈1-838x1024.png 838w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/朋友圈1-768x939.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/朋友圈1-1256x1536.png 1256w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/朋友圈1-1080x1320.png 1080w\" si